    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock for precise torque distribution. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity during high-lateral-G maneuvers. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing replacement, maintaining the high-strung engine's internal tolerances. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical synchronization of the double-VANOS system and throttle response remains razor-sharp.",
